# Optional: [Cloudflare Web Analytics](https://developers.cloudflare.com/web-analytics/)
# Register host "goliathuy.github.io" in the Cloudflare dashboard, then paste the public token.
# The built HTML includes the token in the page (same for everyone); omit this for no analytics.
# VITE_CF_WEB_ANALYTICS_TOKEN=

# Optional: Open Graph image for /kegel/ (1920×1440 mockup at site root, same as portfolio card).
# Does not add analytics; only link-preview cards. Omit to skip og:image in the Kegel build.
# VITE_KEGEL_OG_IMAGE=https://goliathuy.github.io/KegelTimerMockup.png
